1#L32" class="inline-onebox" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">LaserCAN/docs/example-java.md at master · GrappleRobotics/LaserCAN · GitHub</a></p>
<p>Looks like you need to replace</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">public void shootOff(){
IntakeSensor.getMeasurement();
if (LaserCan.LASERCAN_STATUS_VALID_MEASUREMENT&lt;=100){
IntakeFeedMotor.set(0);
IntakeCenterMotor.set(0);
LauncherFeedMotor.set(0);
}
}
</code></pre>
<p>With</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">public void shootOff(){
LaserCan.Measurement measurement = lc.getMeasurement();
if (measurement.status == LaserCan.LASERCAN_STATUS_VALID_MEASUREMENT &amp;&amp; measurement.distance_mm &lt;= 100) {
IntakeFeedMotor.set(0);
IntakeCenterMotor.set(0);
LauncherFeedMotor.set(0);
}
}
</code></pre>
